28:13.359 --> 28:15.662
(music playing)

28:19.465 --> 28:22.068
Once.

28:22.102 --> 28:23.136
Many years ago.

28:23.169 --> 28:24.538
What was it?

28:26.640 --> 28:28.575
Assault.
ROLAND: Assault and battery.

28:28.609 --> 28:29.810
You beat up a girlfriend,

28:29.843 --> 28:31.077
didn't you, Mr. Carrington?

28:31.111 --> 28:32.312
I pushed her.

28:32.345 --> 28:34.047
ROLAND: Pushed her
and she was hospitalized

28:34.080 --> 28:36.249
with three broken ribs,

28:36.282 --> 28:37.584
wasn't she, Mr. Carrington?

28:39.520 --> 28:42.455
(music playing)

28:48.862 --> 28:51.264
Did you know
about that conviction?

28:51.297 --> 28:53.033
HERIC: So what?
He was only 19 at the time.

28:53.066 --> 28:54.467
It doesn't matter.

28:54.500 --> 28:55.836
That felony was reason enough

28:55.869 --> 28:57.638
to keep him off the stand.

28:57.671 --> 28:58.772
HERIC: You told me
to put him on.

28:58.805 --> 29:00.674
DONNELL: We didn't know
he beat up a former girlfriend.

29:00.707 --> 29:02.676
HERIC: Well, the jury
had to hear his story.

29:02.709 --> 29:03.644
DONNELL: How about you
letting us in

29:03.677 --> 29:05.311
on all the facts from now on?

29:06.713 --> 29:09.716
Just help me prepare
my closing.

29:09.750 --> 29:11.217
We'll meet you back
at the office.

29:17.924 --> 29:20.761
I have no information
whatsoever.

29:20.794 --> 29:21.928
What's your relationship

29:21.962 --> 29:23.263
with Mr. Mathis?

29:23.296 --> 29:24.731
I work with him.
We're both lawyers

29:24.765 --> 29:25.832
in the same firm.

29:25.866 --> 29:27.167
BERLUTI:
Do you socialize together?

29:27.200 --> 29:28.334
MARK: No, we do not.

29:28.368 --> 29:30.436
Were you in the
Palmer House Hotel

29:30.470 --> 29:32.338
on the evening of April 12th?

29:32.372 --> 29:34.274
No, I was not.

29:34.307 --> 29:35.275
BERLUTI: Do you have
any information

29:35.308 --> 29:36.442
concerning the events

29:36.476 --> 29:37.911
involving Mr. Mathis

29:37.944 --> 29:38.812
on April 12th?

29:38.845 --> 29:39.646
Asked and answered.

29:39.680 --> 29:42.115
MARK: I will answer it again.

29:42.148 --> 29:43.917
I don't know
what you're talking about,

29:43.950 --> 29:45.852
and I have no information.

29:47.721 --> 29:49.189
Do you know Jennifer Cole?

29:49.222 --> 29:50.557
No, I do not.

29:50.591 --> 29:52.158
Ever heard of her before?

29:52.192 --> 29:53.527
Only in connection

29:53.560 --> 29:54.427
with this lawsuit.

29:59.499 --> 30:00.601
Okay.

30:00.634 --> 30:02.703
We're done.

30:02.736 --> 30:03.904
You can go, Mark.

30:06.206 --> 30:07.407
You also, please.

30:12.045 --> 30:13.046
If you go forward

30:13.079 --> 30:15.481
with this lawsuit,
Mr. Berluti,

30:15.516 --> 30:16.917
this is the counterclaim

30:16.950 --> 30:18.685
that awaits you.

30:18.719 --> 30:20.253
Never mind abuse of process.

30:20.286 --> 30:21.622
There are counts of libel,

30:21.655 --> 30:23.023
defamation of character.

30:23.056 --> 30:25.659
You can't sue me for what I
allege in a complaint.

30:25.692 --> 30:27.360
MATHIS: Oh, we will.

30:27.393 --> 30:28.695
And, truthfully,
I hope we lose

30:28.729 --> 30:30.396
the first go-round.

30:30.430 --> 30:31.297
That'll give us a chance

30:31.331 --> 30:32.599
to go to the appeals court,

30:32.633 --> 30:35.435
possibly the S. J. C.

30:35.468 --> 30:36.670
I hope you like working

30:36.703 --> 30:38.572
on this case, Mr. Berluti,

30:38.605 --> 30:41.207
because for the next
three years,

30:41.241 --> 30:43.076
you'll have time
for little else.

30:44.978 --> 30:47.013
(door opens)

30:47.047 --> 30:48.048
Sorry we're late.

30:48.081 --> 30:49.783
We were held up in court,
and we all wanted

30:49.816 --> 30:51.552
to come over together.
What is this?

30:51.585 --> 30:53.854
YOUNG: This is an army,
Mr. Mathis.

30:53.887 --> 30:56.823
(music playing)

31:01.962 --> 31:03.296
YOUNG: See, you may have thought
to yourself,

31:03.329 --> 31:05.065
"Nobody's gonna take up
the cause

31:05.098 --> 31:06.700
of a lowly prostitute,"

31:06.733 --> 31:08.468
but you were wrong.

31:08.501 --> 31:10.871
Jennifer Cole is a friend
of this firm.

31:10.904 --> 31:12.506
We care about Jennifer Cole.

31:12.539 --> 31:14.340
We stand committed
to exercising

31:14.374 --> 31:15.709
Jennifer Cole's rights.

31:15.742 --> 31:18.311
I guess what I'm trying
to say, Mr. Mathis,

31:18.344 --> 31:20.080
if you want a war,

31:20.113 --> 31:22.348
you've got one.

31:22.382 --> 31:23.817
MATHIS: You think
you're ready to challenge

31:23.850 --> 31:25.652
the resources
of this law firm?

31:25.686 --> 31:27.187
Do some research.

31:27.220 --> 31:28.955
We've been up
against big firms before

31:28.989 --> 31:31.758
and beaten them
for a lot of money.

31:31.792 --> 31:34.494
A reputation
is a terrible thing to waste,

31:34.528 --> 31:36.062
Mr. Mathis.

31:36.096 --> 31:37.864
You people are what give lawyers

31:37.898 --> 31:39.332
a bad name.

31:39.365 --> 31:41.101
WASHINGTON:
No, lawyers who rape

31:41.134 --> 31:42.903
give us a bad name.

31:42.936 --> 31:43.837
DONNELL: Look,

31:43.870 --> 31:45.171
we can fight

31:45.205 --> 31:46.607
or we can settle this,

31:46.640 --> 31:48.441
but like Eugene Young said,

31:48.474 --> 31:50.176
if it's a fight you want,

31:50.210 --> 31:51.845
you're in for a big one.

31:51.878 --> 31:54.180
And, win or lose,

31:54.214 --> 31:55.448
you lose.

31:55.481 --> 31:58.451
(music playing)

32:05.025 --> 32:07.961
(music playing)

32:13.233 --> 32:16.402
$175,000,

32:16.436 --> 32:19.139
all conditioned
on total confidentiality.

32:21.141 --> 32:23.109
A hundred and seventy-five
thousand?

32:23.143 --> 32:24.911
I think we should take it.

32:24.945 --> 32:26.680
Okay.

32:26.713 --> 32:29.315
We'll have the check tomorrow.

32:29.349 --> 32:30.316
Thank you.

32:32.118 --> 32:33.053
Thank you.

32:33.086 --> 32:34.054
Thank you all.

32:39.760 --> 32:41.762
But, Jennifer, listen.

32:47.100 --> 32:48.802
This guy, Mathis,

32:48.835 --> 32:51.104
if he's capable of rape,

32:51.137 --> 32:53.239
we just left him pretty hot.

32:53.273 --> 32:54.808
I don't want you ever...

32:54.841 --> 32:56.677
going back to the Palmer House.

32:56.710 --> 32:58.645
I won't.

32:58.679 --> 33:00.246
BERLUTI: You have a little girl,
Jennifer.

33:00.280 --> 33:02.015
She needs you.

33:02.048 --> 33:03.183
The other night,

33:03.216 --> 33:04.217
you could have been killed.

33:06.052 --> 33:08.822
You need to start over.

33:08.855 --> 33:12.025
I will, Jimmy,

33:12.058 --> 33:13.126
and not just for her,

33:13.159 --> 33:14.595
but for you.

33:14.628 --> 33:15.929
You don't owe me nothing.

33:15.962 --> 33:18.298
I owe you my life, Jimmy,

33:20.000 --> 33:21.501
and I'll never forget it.

33:23.570 --> 33:26.507
(music playing)

33:37.483 --> 33:38.318
ROLAND: She told her husband

33:38.351 --> 33:40.821
she feared Daniel Carrington,

33:40.854 --> 33:42.756
feared that he might hurt her,

33:42.789 --> 33:45.091
and she's found dead.

33:45.125 --> 33:46.860
Dead with traces
of Daniel Carrington's

33:46.893 --> 33:48.428
semen in her.

33:48.461 --> 33:49.362
Her blood is found

33:49.395 --> 33:51.131
in Daniel Carrington's car.

33:51.164 --> 33:52.899
Come on.

33:52.933 --> 33:54.367
He previously beat up

33:54.400 --> 33:57.203
and hospitalized
another girlfriend.

33:57.237 --> 33:58.238
All the evidence

33:58.271 --> 34:00.173
in this case points to him,

34:00.206 --> 34:01.975
and what's his story?

34:02.008 --> 34:04.110
They made love in a bar?

34:05.846 --> 34:07.581
Nobody saw them in this bar,

34:07.614 --> 34:09.315
not one patron,

34:09.349 --> 34:11.451
not one waitress or bartender.

34:11.484 --> 34:13.485
There was a message

34:13.520 --> 34:14.621
from the victim

34:14.655 --> 34:16.255
breaking off the relationship.

34:16.289 --> 34:17.558
A message...

34:17.591 --> 34:19.693
to the defendant
left one hour

34:19.726 --> 34:21.895
before she was murdered.

34:21.928 --> 34:25.031
There is no doubt here,

34:25.065 --> 34:27.634
ladies and gentlemen.

34:27.668 --> 34:29.268
Daniel Carrington

34:29.302 --> 34:31.271
murdered Jean Homestead.

34:41.147 --> 34:43.049
I certainly understand
the theory

34:43.083 --> 34:44.985
that Danny did it.

34:45.018 --> 34:46.520
His sperm,

34:46.553 --> 34:47.688
the blood,

34:47.721 --> 34:49.155
phone message,

34:49.188 --> 34:50.524
it makes perfect sense

34:50.556 --> 34:51.925
to jump to that conclusion,

34:51.958 --> 34:52.693
doesn't it?

34:52.726 --> 34:54.695
But we don't jump
to conclusions

34:54.728 --> 34:56.161
in murder trials.

34:56.196 --> 34:59.499
The evidence
has to establish guilt

34:59.533 --> 35:01.902
beyond all reasonable doubt.

35:01.935 --> 35:04.738
Now, have they really done
so here?

35:04.771 --> 35:06.507
They certainly didn't rule out

35:06.540 --> 35:08.174
that they made love at the club

35:08.208 --> 35:12.078
or that Danny was alone at home.

35:12.112 --> 35:13.279
And let's face it.

35:13.313 --> 35:15.415
We really can't rule out
the husband,

35:15.448 --> 35:16.182
can we?

35:16.216 --> 35:18.184
He had motive,

35:18.218 --> 35:19.686
opportunity,

35:19.720 --> 35:21.421
no alibi.

35:21.454 --> 35:22.589
What about the stepson,

35:22.623 --> 35:23.690
for that matter?

35:23.724 --> 35:25.291
Hmm? Any stepson

35:25.325 --> 35:28.862
embroiled in an Oedipal affair

35:28.895 --> 35:31.898
is certainly capable
of twisted turns.

35:31.932 --> 35:34.300
It doesn't even stop there.

35:34.334 --> 35:35.936
Suppose Danny Carrington

35:35.969 --> 35:38.939
had another lover.

35:38.972 --> 35:41.474
No evidence, to be sure,
but they

35:41.508 --> 35:43.209
didn't even investigate that.

35:43.243 --> 35:46.412
And is it really
that far-fetched?

35:46.446 --> 35:47.714
The other lover

35:47.748 --> 35:49.916
gets wind of the little session

35:49.950 --> 35:51.785
at the club,

35:51.818 --> 35:54.521
goes to the victim's house,

35:54.555 --> 35:56.022
threatens her,

35:56.056 --> 35:58.725
forces her to make
that phone call

35:58.759 --> 36:00.360
to implicate Danny.

36:00.393 --> 36:03.396
Then he or she kills the woman,

36:03.429 --> 36:04.698
dumps her in the alley,

36:04.731 --> 36:06.366
knowing full well

36:06.399 --> 36:09.503
who the police will blame.

36:09.536 --> 36:11.171
He or she even plants

36:11.204 --> 36:13.674
that little blood speck
in his car.

36:16.076 --> 36:20.113
Now, Danny is
the obvious suspect,

36:20.146 --> 36:22.849
but it could have been anybody,

36:22.883 --> 36:24.250
maybe one of you,

36:26.486 --> 36:28.088
maybe the judge,

36:31.558 --> 36:32.593
maybe me.

36:32.626 --> 36:35.562
(music playing)

36:38.031 --> 36:38.799
Now,

36:38.832 --> 36:39.866
could have been a bonehead,

36:39.900 --> 36:41.835
stupid murder by Danny

36:42.936 --> 36:45.405
or one of the more
perfect variety

36:45.438 --> 36:47.941
by somebody else to frame him,

36:47.974 --> 36:49.510
the husband,

36:49.543 --> 36:50.844
the stepson,

36:50.877 --> 36:52.646
a female lover,

36:52.679 --> 36:54.615
a big, gay,

36:54.648 --> 36:56.850
sick lover, anybody.

36:58.184 --> 37:00.220
The simple truth is,

37:01.555 --> 37:03.524
we don't know,

37:03.557 --> 37:05.158
certainly not beyond

37:05.191 --> 37:07.828
all reasonable doubt.

37:09.395 --> 37:12.332
(music playing)

37:39.626 --> 37:41.427
They sent you with the check?

37:41.461 --> 37:44.731
No, the check is coming
by messenger.

37:44.765 --> 37:48.602
May I see you in private,
Mr. Berluti?

37:48.635 --> 37:50.571
(door locks)

37:53.339 --> 37:55.542
I'm a man of conscience,

37:55.576 --> 37:56.643
which made yesterday

37:56.677 --> 37:58.444
one of the most difficult days
in my life.

38:01.414 --> 38:03.917
I lied in my deposition,
Mr. Berluti.

38:05.218 --> 38:06.252
I had a hunch.

38:06.286 --> 38:08.589
I don't think you had this
particular hunch.

38:11.191 --> 38:12.458
About six weeks ago,

38:12.492 --> 38:13.560
I met Jennifer Cole

38:13.594 --> 38:15.095
in the Palmer House.

38:15.128 --> 38:16.029
She passed herself off

38:16.062 --> 38:18.699
as a young advertising
executive.

38:18.732 --> 38:21.034
We got a room, we made love,

38:21.067 --> 38:22.435
after which, she informed me

38:22.468 --> 38:24.470
that she was a prostitute

38:24.505 --> 38:26.740
and if I didn't give her
$10,000,

38:26.773 --> 38:29.643
she would tell my wife

38:29.676 --> 38:31.645
or cry "Rape."

38:35.749 --> 38:36.917
Here's a copy of my check.

38:41.121 --> 38:42.122
There's nothing to be done now.

38:42.155 --> 38:44.390
Your case is settled.

38:44.424 --> 38:45.425
But these are people

38:45.458 --> 38:46.760
with families,

38:46.793 --> 38:49.162
Mr. Berluti.

38:49.195 --> 38:51.798
It's difficult for me
to stay quiet

38:51.832 --> 38:53.834
knowing she's going
to do this again.

38:56.102 --> 38:59.039
(door opens and closes)

39:06.312 --> 39:07.447
Did you kill her?

39:07.480 --> 39:09.616
HERIC: Bobby, I was throwing out
a hypothetical.

39:09.650 --> 39:11.217
DONNELL:
I don't think so, Joey.

39:11.251 --> 39:14.354
This totally fits
your narcissistic disorder.

39:14.387 --> 39:15.789
The only reason
we were at that table

39:15.822 --> 39:18.058
was to be an audience
for that smile.

39:18.091 --> 39:19.425
You did it,

39:19.459 --> 39:21.094
and you wanted us to know
you did it.

39:21.127 --> 39:22.729
HERIC: You've been watching
too much television.

39:22.763 --> 39:24.565
DONNELL: Did you and Danny
used to be lovers?

39:24.598 --> 39:26.166
Well, now that you mention it,

39:26.199 --> 39:28.735
that's how I got the case.

39:28.769 --> 39:29.736
DONNELL: I'm going to the D. A.

39:29.770 --> 39:31.137
HERIC: Oh, please, Bobby.

39:31.171 --> 39:32.539
The jury's out.

39:32.573 --> 39:34.007
If we win,
you've got nothing to say.

39:34.040 --> 39:35.709
If we lose,

39:35.742 --> 39:37.210
well, D. A. s just love

39:37.243 --> 39:38.411
to throw out convictions,
don't they?

39:38.444 --> 39:40.413
I'm sure he'll be thrilled
to listen.

39:40.446 --> 39:41.948
FRUTT: I think you wanna lose.

39:41.982 --> 39:44.317
That's why you put your guy
on the stand

39:44.350 --> 39:46.019
with a felony conviction

39:46.052 --> 39:47.588
and that closing?
HERIC: Well, wait, wait.

39:47.621 --> 39:48.955
What was wrong
with my closing?

39:48.989 --> 39:50.290
FRUTT: It was ridiculous.

39:50.323 --> 39:51.558
"Maybe the judge did it,

39:51.592 --> 39:52.492
maybe a juror did it?"

39:52.526 --> 39:54.260
I also said,
"Maybe the lawyer did it."

39:54.294 --> 39:56.062
That part, you seem to believe.

39:56.096 --> 39:56.730
DONNELL: You killed her.

39:56.763 --> 39:57.397
HERIC: Bobby,

39:57.430 --> 40:01.301
Bobby (chuckles) Bobby,

40:01.334 --> 40:03.269
you think I'm evil?

40:03.303 --> 40:05.005
DONNELL: You murdered his lover,

40:05.038 --> 40:06.439
framed him,

40:06.472 --> 40:07.908
got yourself put on
as his lawyer

40:07.941 --> 40:10.176
to guarantee he goes away.

40:11.812 --> 40:13.647
Well, I must say, it does sound

40:13.680 --> 40:15.081
worthy of me.

40:15.115 --> 40:18.084
(music playing)

40:23.456 --> 40:24.390
Hi, everybody.

40:29.229 --> 40:30.831
(laughs) What's the matter?

40:33.834 --> 40:35.101
The name "Mark Greene"

40:35.135 --> 40:36.903
didn't ring a bell with you,
Jennifer?

40:39.673 --> 40:40.741
You cashed his check.

40:45.211 --> 40:46.980
You did the same thing to him

40:47.013 --> 40:48.214
you did to Mathis.

40:52.753 --> 40:54.955
Here's your check.

40:54.988 --> 40:56.489
Take it,

40:56.523 --> 40:57.924
walk out of this office,

40:57.958 --> 40:59.425
and never come back here again.

41:01.862 --> 41:03.697
These people are rich, Jimmy.

41:05.098 --> 41:06.600
It's expensive

41:06.633 --> 41:08.134
raising a child, and...

41:08.168 --> 41:10.036
BERLUTI: The biggest problem
your child has

41:10.070 --> 41:11.805
is having you for a mother.

41:14.808 --> 41:18.078
If I hear of this happening
ever again,

41:18.111 --> 41:20.213
I'll go to the police

41:20.246 --> 41:22.315
and to Social Services

41:22.348 --> 41:24.217
to take that child away
from you.

41:26.820 --> 41:28.154
Take the check,

41:28.188 --> 41:29.122
walk out,

41:29.155 --> 41:30.824
and never come back.

41:30.857 --> 41:33.794
(music playing)

41:55.649 --> 41:56.917
I'm so nervous.

41:56.950 --> 41:58.451
PATRICK: Will the defendant
please rise?

42:01.988 --> 42:03.089
Madam foreperson,

42:03.123 --> 42:06.059
has the jury reached
a unanimous verdict?

42:06.092 --> 42:07.360
We have, Your Honor.

42:07.393 --> 42:09.195
What say you?

42:09.229 --> 42:10.597
FOREPERSON: In the matter
of the Commonwealth

42:10.631 --> 42:12.365
versus Daniel Carrington,

42:12.398 --> 42:13.934
on the charge of murder

42:13.967 --> 42:15.602
in the first degree,

42:15.636 --> 42:17.337
we, the jury,
find the defendant,

42:17.370 --> 42:19.940
Daniel Carrington,

42:19.973 --> 42:20.907
guilty.

42:24.778 --> 42:25.846
HERIC: We will appeal,
Your Honor.

42:25.879 --> 42:26.913
So noted.

42:26.947 --> 42:28.014
Members of the jury,

42:28.048 --> 42:29.082
this completes your service.

42:29.115 --> 42:30.817
Security, will you take

42:30.851 --> 42:32.385
the defendant into custody?

42:32.418 --> 42:33.419
We're hereby adjourned.

42:33.453 --> 42:35.756
(gavel bangs)

42:35.789 --> 42:36.890
HERIC: Danny, listen,
don't lose hope.

42:36.923 --> 42:38.825
We will keep trying.
But what happens now, right?

42:38.859 --> 42:39.760
HERIC: We're gonna come
right in.

42:39.793 --> 42:41.528
We're gonna start talking
about our appeal.

42:41.562 --> 42:43.429
Now, Danny, don't lose hope.

42:43.463 --> 42:44.931
Don't lose hope, Danny.

42:44.965 --> 42:45.932
Remember,

42:45.966 --> 42:47.167
in the end,

42:47.200 --> 42:48.234
it's a good world.

42:53.540 --> 42:54.374
Well,

42:54.407 --> 42:57.243
I guess you can't win them all.

42:57.277 --> 43:00.146
If I can figure out a way
to reveal what I know, I will.

43:00.180 --> 43:01.281
HERIC: Certainly you know
the allegation

43:01.314 --> 43:03.316
that I tried to lose a case

43:03.349 --> 43:05.351
would be libel, per se.

43:06.787 --> 43:08.955
Listen, come on,
sometimes you have to accept

43:08.989 --> 43:10.891
unfortunate outcomes.

43:10.924 --> 43:13.760
All part of being a lawyer,
isn't it?

43:13.794 --> 43:16.029
Right, Ellie?

43:16.062 --> 43:17.063
